subject: Prices (Fares, Fees and Rates)
Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Nascar lowered the fee it charges racetracks to hold races, a move that should allow track owners to reduce ticket prices and lower various fees associated with holding a race.
